.TH "lsm_pool_total_space_get" 3 "lsm_pool_total_space_get" "October 2017" "Libstoragemgmt C API Manual" 
.SH NAME
lsm_pool_total_space_get \- Retrieves the total space for the pool.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "uint64_t" lsm_pool_total_space_get
.BI "(lsm_pool *" p ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "p" 12
Pool to retrieve total space for.
.SH "VERSION"
1.0
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Retrieves the total space in bytes for the pool.
.SH "RETURN"
uint64_t. 0 if argument 'p' is NULL or not a valid lsm_pool pointer.
